#lg C	kirugu


@(C.39 = 39-46) O city, the lament is bitter, the lament made for you. Your lament is bitter, O city, the lament made for you. In his righteous destroyed city its lament is bitter. In his righteous destroyed @wSN{Urim}, the lament is bitter, the lament made for you. Your lament is bitter, O city, the lament made for you. In his destroyed @wSN{Urim} its lament is bitter. How long will your bitter lament grieve your lord who weeps? How long will your bitter lament grieve @wDN{Nanna} who weeps?

@(C.47 = 47-55) O brick-built @wSN{Urim}, the lament is bitter, the lament made for you. O @wTN{E-kiš-nu-ŋal}, your lament is bitter, the lament made for you. O shrine @wTN{Agrun-kug}, the lament is bitter, the lament made for you. O great place @wTN{Ki-ur}, the lament is bitter, the lament made for you. O shrine @wSN{Nibru}, city, the lament is bitter, the lament made for you. O brick-built @wTN{E-kur}, the lament is bitter, the lament made for you. O @wTN{Ŋa-ŋiš-šua}, the lament is bitter, the lament made for you. O @wTN{Ubšu-unkena}, the lament is bitter, the lament made for you. O brick-built @wSN{Iri-kug}, the lament is bitter, the lament made for you.

@(C.56 = 56-63) O @wTN{E-tar-sirsir}, the lament is bitter, the lament made for you. O @wTN{Ma-gu-ena}, the lament is bitter, the lament made for you. O brick-built @wSN{Isin}, the lament is bitter, the lament made for you. O shrine @wTN{Egal-maḫ}, the lament is bitter, the lament made for you. O brick-built @wSN{Unug}, the lament is bitter, the lament made for you. O brick-built @wDN{Eridug}, the lament is bitter, the lament made for you. How long will your bitter lament grieve your lord who weeps? How long will your bitter lament grieve @wDN{Nanna} who weeps?

@(C.64 = 64-71) O city, your name exists but you have been destroyed. O city, your wall rises high but your Land has perished. O my city, like an innocent ewe your lamb has been torn from you. O @wSN{Urim}, like an innocent goat your kid has perished. O city, your rites have been alienated from you, your powers have been changed into alien powers. How long will your bitter lament grieve your lord who weeps? How long will your bitter lament grieve @wDN{Nanna} who weeps?

